From c9afdc2d41e1be298438ffb46ed2f87d5ca5550a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 08:16:05 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] feat: add PWA offline support with Service Worker and
 background sync

- Service Worker caches static assets on install; network-first for API GETs
- manifest.json and icon.svg enable PWA install prompt on mobile browsers
- Offline practice logging queues sessions to localStorage and syncs automatically when network returns
- Online/offline banner shows current connectivity status
- processOfflineQueue runs on app start and on 'online' event for reliable sync

https://claude.ai/code/session_01GnX385cSM8TFePkRcyYiKM
