From 1532cf556f9f20572237f29fe6361c9e31630496 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 13:36:05 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] feat: add training program generator with 100 yoga poses
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- poses.js: 100 yoga poses with metadata (energy, difficulty, time-of-day,
  intensity, phase) and stick-figure parameters for SVG rendering
- pose-svg.js: parameterized stick-figure SVG renderer (single function
  generates any pose from joint angles, ~3KB total)
- Program generator: 3-step builder (time / intensity / duration) produces
  warmup → main → cooldown sequence with no duplicates, ordered by category
- Guided mode: full-screen practice with circular timer, breath cue,
  pose name, next pose preview
- Recent programs saved to localStorage; auto-logs as yoga session on finish
- Updates Service Worker cache to v2 to include new assets
